# Instructions

## Install

```bash
# Configure custom ROS repository
echo "deb [trusted=yes] @REPO_URL@ ./" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/@DISTRO_NAME@.list

# Install and setup rosdep
sudo apt update
sudo apt install python3-rosdep
sudo rosdep init

# Define custom rosdep mapping
echo "yaml @REPO_URL@/rosdep.yaml @DEB_DISTRO@" | sudo tee /etc/ros/rosdep/sources.list.d/1-@DISTRO_NAME@.list
rosdep update
```
